Converted xml netconf reply to json using pyang. Following is the json output which seems wrong as per yang json format. x-module prefix should not be included for child "upstream-data-rate-profile" as it is already included for its parent "configs".

{
"x-module:configs": {
"profiles": {
"x-module:profile": [
{ "name": "default-profile", "maximum": 50000, "maximum-rate": 50000, "minimum": 2000, "minimum-rate": 2000 }
]
}
